                            <comment id="16196715" author="lorenz.quack" created="Mon, 9 Oct 2017 09:12:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The SCRAM SASL implementation was ported from the AMQP 0-x client to the new AMQP 1.0 client. This porting included this bug.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
